  "blurb": "A high-floor, three-bedroom premium residence of around 131 m² in a gated beachside enclave at Laguna, Bang Tao, Phuket. Light, west-facing interiors open onto a deep semi-open lanai framing treetops and glimpses of the Andaman horizon, with a residents' rooftop deck and beach lounge moments from the sand. Minimum stay seven nights.",
  "detail": "Set on the upper premium levels of a low-rise beachside enclave at Laguna, Bang Tao, this three-bedroom home spans roughly 131 square metres — about 92 of refined, air-conditioned interior wrapped by a generous 35–38 m² semi-open lanai. The west-facing aspect carries afternoon light deep into the living spaces and out over a canopy of trees, with glimpses of the Andaman horizon beyond.\n\nThe lanai is the heart of the home: wide enough for both a lounge and a full dining setting, it blurs the line between inside and out and turns every evening toward the sunset. Indoors, an open-plan living and dining room flows to a fitted kitchen, while three bedrooms — two en-suite, plus a third bathroom — make it easy for a family or two couples to spread out. Sleeps up to five.\n\nResidents share a quietly luxurious set of facilities: a panoramic rooftop recreation deck, a private members-only beach lounge for sunset gatherings, swimming pools and landscaped gardens. The enclave sits among Phuket's most connected addresses — a short stroll to Bang Tao Beach and minutes from Boat Avenue, Porto de Phuket and the Laguna golf course, with the island's dining, marinas and international schools close at hand.\n\nOffered for stays of seven nights or more as a fully serviced residence, with air-conditioning, in-residence laundry, daily-living essentials and an in-app concierge.",
